snippet.title: Storm Shelter - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Made for the Brackeys Game Jam in 1 week, Storm Shelter is a mix between Tetris and autobattlers. Build a house for the Guy and see if it can withstand a storm of bizarre storm-themed enemies!

Play it here: https://dragonaero.itch.io/stormshelter

MORE DRAGONAERO: https://linktr.ee/dragonaero
WEBSITE: dragonaero64.github.io
OFFICIAL ACCOUNTS: bit.ly/DA-Accounts
